data.name: Alchemy Ingredients
data.description: Alchemy Ingredients offers a portfolio of 100% natural ingredients developed to provide an easy and effective way to thicken oil or water based systems. Based on sugar chemistry and Ecocert/Cosmos approved, Alchemy Ingredients is committed to continuous research and development, and has a portfolio of products that have been developed to meet the needs of customers and solve formulation problems.

data.name: Instathix
data.description: Instathix® is a synergistic blend of powders that act as an easy-to-use emulsifier.

data.name: Clearthix
data.description: Clearthix is a versatile, cost effective, transparent water thickener based on Cellulose and Alginate.

data.name: Sclerothix
data.description: Sclerothix® is a 100% natural water thickener which makes transparent, rich, smooth gels suitable for a variety of uses including suspending particles and thickening some surfactant systems. It can be used on its own or as part of an emulsion or surfactant formula.

data.name: Sucragel
data.description: 100% natural emulsifier and oil thickener based on sugar chemistry.

data.name: HIPEgel
data.description: HIPEgel® enables the formulator to make high oil HIPEs (High Internal Phase Emulsions) easily, at room temperature. The oil phase is typically greater than 90% and the resulting emulsion is o/w, meaning that the formula is light and has a ‘quick break’ effect. Due to the nature of the polygonal packing of oil droplets in the structure, stable viscous systems are made without the use of added thickeners.

data.name: Sucrabase
data.description: 100% natural, ready-to-use cosmetic gel bases.

data.name: Sucrablend
data.description: 100% natural and COSMOS approved temperature stability additive. Supplied as a fine white powder, it is designed to be used at 0.5-2% with Sucragel® to improve high temperature stability.

data.name: Sapogel
data.description: Sapogel Q is a liquid blend which acts as a natural oil thickening agent to make balm textures.

data.name: Sucragel® CF
data.description: Sucragel CF is a liquid which acts as natural oil thickening agent and cold process emulsifier.

data.name: Sapogel® Q
data.description: Sapogel Q is a liquid blend which acts as a natural oil thickening agent to make balm textures.

data.name: Sucragel® XL
data.description: Sucragel® XL is a liquid which acts as natural oil thickening agent and cold process emulsifier. The product is manufactured from raw materials of strictly vegetable origin.

data.name: HIPEgel® Oleo C
data.description: HIPEgel® Oleo C is a COSMOS-approved version of HIPEgel® Oleo which enables the formulator to make high oil HIPEs (High Internal Phase Emulsions) easily, at room temperature. The oil phase is typically greater than 90% and the resulting emulsion is o/w, meaning that the formula is light and has a ‘quick break’ effect. Due to the nature of the polygonal packing of oil droplets in the structure, stable viscous systems are made without the use of added thickeners.

data.name: Sucragel® AOF Bio
data.description: Sucragel AOF Bio is a liquid which acts as natural oil thickening agent and cold process emulsifier.

data.name: Sucragel® AP V2
data.description: Sucragel AP V2 is a liquid which acts as a natural oil thickening agent and cold process emulsifier.

data.name: Sucrathix VX
data.description: Sucrathix VX is a synergistic blend of powders which perform as a water gelling agent.

data.name: Sucrabase C
data.description: Sucrabase C is a thick oily gel which immediately turns into a thin emulsion on addition of water. It can be used to create a number of different formulations by simply stirring in other ingredients at room temperature.

data.name: Sucrabase SF Bio
data.description: Sucrabase SF Bio is a thick oily gel which immediately turns into a thin emulsion on addition of water. It can be used to create a number of different formulations by simply stirring in other ingredients at room temperature.
